reviewText: Very good movie on the heros behind the animal rescue work done after Katrina.  So much was done and you will realize this and have a great appreciation for these men and woman.
This is one heartwarming documentary for any Animal Lover! Very touching yet very sad! Great movie for someone that's interested in Animal Rescues!
GREAT storytelling filled with poignant details and interesting people, and an important piece of history I wouldn't have known about otherwise. Very well done. P.S. Keep the tissue box handy. :)
